      "system": {
        "description": {
          "value": "<p>Observant PCs may notice Dreyfus's tells: he never blinks, he watches mouths more than hands, he does not eat (his bowl has been full for days), he does not sleep, and his ears flatten in <em>attention</em>&mdash;not fear&mdash;when he hears the word 'Kaelen.' A Hard Intuition test reveals that something is deeply wrong with this animal.</p>",
